                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <div class="team-photo">
                        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhibmotzx/image/upload/v1741540353/viber_image_2025-03-09_19-12-06-581_xg6prx.jpg" alt="Sarah Johnson">
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-info">
                        <h3>Ivan Mitkov</h3>
