                    </div>
                    <div class="team-info">
                        <h3>Asia Mitkova</h3>
                        <div class="team-role">Chief Technology Officer</div>
                        <p class="team-bio">Asialeads our digital transformation initiatives, developing innovative solutions to enhance the customer experience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Our Locations</h2>
            <div class="about-content">
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhibmotzx/image/upload/v1741540758/sddefault_ry5vzr.jpg" alt="Fast Drive Location">
                </div>
                <div class="about-text">
                    <p>We currently operate from three strategic locations across Dubai:</p>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Dubai Marina Branch</strong><br>
                        Our flagship location in the heart of Dubai Marina offers our full range of vehicles and services.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Dubai International Airport</strong><br>
                        Conveniently located at Terminal 3 for seamless pickups and returns for travelers.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Downtown Dubai</strong><br>
                        Our newest branch near Dubai Mall caters to tourists and business travelers in the downtown area.
                    </p>
                    <p>All our locations are open 24/7 to accommodate your schedule, with dedicated staff ready to assist you at any time.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

